Name: Jelly In The Dark
About the game: [h2Escape from the Ant Kingdom full of ants![/h2] You are a fragrant and delicious jelly in an ant's den, and you are currently wanted. The goal is to survive somehow. Survive and escape. It's a must to apply soil to hide the smell! Let's shovel the soil piled up all over the map and use it. If you run out of dirt gauges and get caught... there will be a big trouble. Various endings that change with a small choice Let's collect more than 20 endings. Let's make the ending collection rate 100%. There is not one way out Ant Kingdom is wider than you think and there are many places to go. Maybe getting out isn't the only answer... Unique items Collect items and use them wisely Let's find ingenious ways to use it!
